  N5 --> Z1[Outcome: Conflict-free, executable production schedule aligned to inbound materials and supplier lead times; reduced stockouts and obsolescence; minimized expediting costs where possible; prioritized fulfillment of high-margin SKUs; clear exceptions for planner review.]
